Paying for fuel with the license plate means the easiest and most frictionless experience. We will make card payment and the right fuel pump ready for you automatically when you enter a Circle K station and stop by the fuel pump.

- Frictionless

You don’t need to locate your payment card and verify with a PIN for each fuel transaction, it’s all taken care of through the app.

- Easy to use

Simply download the app, sign in with your Circle K extra account, enter your payment card details and license plate number, and you are ready to go. If you do not have Circle K account, it is easy to sign up.

- Safe

The technology is safe, similar solutions are used in parking garages, toll roads and mobile pay solutions.

- How it works

When you enter our stations, a camera will read your license plate and activate the fuel pump next to your car, using the payment card you have entered in the app. You can choose if you want to approve each transaction by clicking once on your smartphone or if you want the process to be completely automatic. Once the transaction is complete you will get a receipt to your smartphone. 

Pay for fuel with license plate will be gradually rolled out across Circle K  network, starting with Sweden in 2021.
